  "notes": {
    "compositionRules": [
      "Every product composes from shared platform capabilities (agdp, evtp, oads, obim, scau).",
      "Session Orchestration (seor) and Metering/Rating (mrtl) are foundational transaction primitives reused across all products.",
      "Roaming capabilities (rhig, rted, pama) are composable into CPMS, eMSP, and Fleet offerings.",
      "Tariff (tapm) and Billing (bisl) remain separable to enable monetization flexibility.",
      "Smart Charging (scen, semc) is an attachable optimization layer on top of CPMS and Fleet products."
    ]
  }
